  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-940f7269-2926-4a4c-891d-833a3d6a0fe1\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-680c0824-768e-4e99-922b-64bae18c87f5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cfcc3f5a-2425-4d3a-9192-110efca01a72\"><span class=\"__se-hash-tag\">#비만</span></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c143b111-e68f-4ae1-bfab-b67ab4983061\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-105c0751-1fe3-47ab-924f-dcf9b6f1f315\">50세 여성분이 비만치료를 위해 내원했습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-38c8328f-00c2-4e17-9dba-33f06ebe3ea0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d80e906d-fe3b-4714-b669-fdbd4f5780ee\">체성분검사 결과를 보니 비만에 체지방도 많습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d628ce6f-9a51-4f6b-9043-d977530efc16\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c24c9924-8cd9-447a-83fb-2eddfbf0a862\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b4f3d0e4-9d28-4562-a811-b22e51fc163b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module se-module-image __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\" \" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b4f3d0e4-9d28-4562-a811-b22e51fc163b\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxOTA3MDJfNDAg/MDAxNTYyMDM1NjA2MjA2.MDLIpmFYTjPcV2Kspz7-SsqdaFlQFWzUznTND1WJRQ8g.BtUIs80ZJqj1Pil_xiEozmXPUPwa_3UtEvNvbWK0zrgg.PNG.isuhani/체성분검사.png\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxOTA3MDJfNDAg/MDAxNTYyMDM1NjA2MjA2.MDLIpmFYTjPcV2Kspz7-SsqdaFlQFWzUznTND1WJRQ8g.BtUIs80ZJqj1Pil_xiEozmXPUPwa_3UtEvNvbWK0zrgg.PNG.isuhani/체성분검사.png?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxOTA3MDJfNDAg/MDAxNTYyMDM1NjA2MjA2.MDLIpmFYTjPcV2Kspz7-SsqdaFlQFWzUznTND1WJRQ8g.BtUIs80ZJqj1Pil_xiEozmXPUPwa_3UtEvNvbWK0zrgg.PNG.isuhani/체성분검사.png?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"177\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                </a>                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4eb023f5-de04-4da3-9e45-0c01ccd0b515\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fbcc6141-c3e8-427a-82d0-e3817aa16003\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-059378c9-187d-4af0-939b-33ae27b022a5\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3f062416-7db1-4340-86a7-55f368b26f01\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8ef1900c-321f-4097-9a83-dbba86df0c7d\">그런데, 근육도 많습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-900656d1-6d0f-47fe-8a72-10bd0a05ae26\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-92f5c02d-45f3-4600-b06f-bf8934ec83bf\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-864c1b84-3b52-472c-9ce6-a36daed112f5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:378px;\">\n\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module se-module-image __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\" \" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-864c1b84-3b52-472c-9ce6-a36daed112f5\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxOTA3MDJfMjgw/MDAxNTYyMDM1NjIyNjg3.nehfPWRK-PdgRFbczwATOaEUTjmxzgyLZkv_7_ErSW4g.zzBfLANVUiG2cAGcJC2e3Isk-PZNVz4YTm4HbFXRwDAg.PNG.isuhani/체성분.png\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxOTA3MDJfMjgw/MDAxNTYyMDM1NjIyNjg3.nehfPWRK-PdgRFbczwATOaEUTjmxzgyLZkv_7_ErSW4g.zzBfLANVUiG2cAGcJC2e3Isk-PZNVz4YTm4HbFXRwDAg.PNG.isuhani/체성분.png?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxOTA3MDJfMjgw/MDAxNTYyMDM1NjIyNjg3.nehfPWRK-PdgRFbczwATOaEUTjmxzgyLZkv_7_ErSW4g.zzBfLANVUiG2cAGcJC2e3Isk-PZNVz4YTm4HbFXRwDAg.PNG.isuhani/체성분.png?type=w580\" data-width=\"378\" data-height=\"174\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                </a>                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ac1b0361-913b-4a20-a725-4ae13586a5f2\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-571a9dea-d259-45ff-a8b7-0e8effd28673\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0340b0b5-c856-46a2-b0fb-349b7a2adf1d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2644e693-895c-47eb-a37d-a121c598f479\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5b791e90-b1a5-4227-8046-2708348c19f8\">물어보니, 에어로빅을 10년 이상 했었다고 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-46f85207-d5b6-4aba-89c0-9f2f671757d8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f16a66e1-1b2a-4684-9eb8-515834a88048\">여자분이긴 하지만, 운동을 많이 했으니 근육이 많을 수도 있겠다 싶습니다.  </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-90456a0c-9b9b-4aaa-8b6f-1e992e7a8d0b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-014fc457-4ca1-44c7-b6c6-e1ddbeba2c11\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bd20d089-3439-49ad-b448-29194e1e495b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-006ad929-6eee-4df5-9e35-58993e6e4ae1\">그런데, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c871e740-8ada-4d46-baea-6644335a653b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-14e46e2d-ab7d-419f-9c3e-254a1fdbfd01\">누워서 진찰을 하는데, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8ba34030-ba1a-4305-bb60-3884217bc0c5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6c206151-cdc4-489e-a1b5-da48ad844270\">임신 막달의 임산부 배 모양입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7c6b41cb-e51d-4044-a2f9-613674fc0ba3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d209906e-c68c-4387-bb3f-827ec8cfba82\">피하지방은 많지 않고 동그랗고 빵빵하게 배가 튀어나와 있습니다. 만지면 딱딱한 느낌. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a4bdba82-72e9-4114-879c-7934c118625a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c1929f32-93a6-4444-95b2-0c031dd4991a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-310c84cb-4f62-45d6-84b8-276a6c2f7bc5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2c08d4a0-f923-4d02-9232-5050c1ccb3f0\"><span class=\"__se-hash-tag\">#다이어트</span></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1ff59938-d8e6-4c2c-9ef2-cd24c4504da8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-db9b0fbe-a609-4037-bcf1-2ec8c045a7ae\">다이어트를 위한 한약을 처방하고, 복부에 지방분해침 시술을 했습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b5fdd92e-f086-4463-9285-5fd9a1947bee\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5e4118b1-497a-412c-a3cd-db379bc16162\">지방분해침은 주 1회 시술. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-54eac24c-b6a5-433e-94c7-d48be9907cb0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5cdbfbe2-1191-4ff7-8a2a-14c63565d1cd\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-834ae4c5-3697-401e-a3bd-3839bb406213\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-977c1deb-78e6-4f7d-9df3-fb3015a91360\">세 번 째 내원했을 때(18일 경과) </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-67c59cc8-11f3-4caa-a562-5cf32b4dc547\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-606b02b1-85ba-4733-8db6-fbd780353760\">체중이 71.1kg 로 3kg 이 줄었으나 배 모양은 똑같습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d13b913a-d01b-4e3e-9b3f-d77ba74e6c28\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-85fc7882-8cd0-42a1-b816-e544520a2ce9\">여전히 딱딱하고 볼록하고 빵빵합니다. 임신 막달의 임산부처럼.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ce123074-f4d4-4ba3-bc84-6dc4e466abcf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-651b62f6-0386-456f-8e08-45169155d888\">다이어트 치료를 해서 3kg 정도 체중이 줄어들면 여러가지 변화가 생깁니다. 배가 물렁물렁 해지거나, 복부 사이즈가 줄어들거나 하는 변화들이죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8895e9b6-85e0-4280-8db0-bfc255a37d5c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8eb8e290-7dd0-4c74-8ce5-6869b5768679\">오랜기간 비만 치료를 하면서 경험한 변화들이 나타나야 하는데, 이 환자분은 그런 변화가 없습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a4823bd0-2476-4770-bc8e-d2f007f3e46a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-062f83e8-0c0d-4952-8e7d-8c74e446e8b0\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5c75c687-54b9-4385-90d4-1ba47930a00a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c30e8bad-d8c0-4d30-aa49-ed757031b3a5\">환자분 차트를 다시 확인했습니다. 2011년도 내원했던 기록을 살펴보니 자궁근종이 있어서 주기적으로 병원을 다닌다는 기록이 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a9bfe3bb-5cfb-4a9f-8cf2-99ceeac8c039\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9b7cd15b-694d-4526-b178-363c2f9706c3\">혹시?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a64391c0-59ab-4872-8856-b6787df5aaeb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-200036ac-ef0e-4488-8faa-dac96f4dbf28\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ee9305a4-db88-4fd0-a4a5-cf48a76bce86\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-31f136ef-d2e8-4a7e-a714-f33f4d460406\"><span class=\"__se-hash-tag\">#종양</span></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ab661a3c-0f35-4e96-bb48-1e18728d34c3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-48162a66-38fe-46ec-bfaa-a79e411a40b3\">환자분께 얘기했습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-03004225-fd7c-4274-a52a-0a1e8d0052a7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0c72d1f3-f9c8-49f4-830a-a2fe4d57c796\">&#x27;환자분의 복부비만은 일반적인 경우가 아닙니다. 복부에 내장지방이 아닌 다른 무언가가 있을 것 같으니 복부  CT 검사를 해보세요&#x27;</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ef26fb20-fc30-464a-b3e9-632cb974c137\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-283dff51-7af5-49f3-a148-569f4097afaf\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6de4a251-cd29-41f3-a279-2f15bfe9e252\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-aa91608b-c1df-4763-bee5-60746fe24b4f\">다행히 환자분이 빠르게 검사를 하셨네요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-511e4ffc-977c-4610-92e2-c34e697542b6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-de052e23-6ab8-42f6-83fe-a341032e939b\">인근 위장전문 병원에서 복부 CT 를 했는데, &quot;빨리 큰 병원 가보시라&quot;는 소견을 들었다고 합니다. ㅜ.ㅠ</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-98e1724e-5376-4286-b566-fc4e2aa6638b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2420eb5a-f270-4b82-8559-0f8929957e20\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4a4e0ffb-4885-4531-8b93-eed22d2c290c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0feef7e7-2bee-47f3-a6ac-57f82b83a6b7\">다시 몇 일의 시간이 흘러 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-72d93450-1ca9-4b74-84ca-45c4fa06e09a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8b9e8d3c-cd3f-4f12-9957-d11fea88b6f1\">성모병원에서 검사를 했더니 30cm 가 넘는 종양이 있어서 바로 수술 일정을 잡고 대기중.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c1d691e9-dd1a-49a8-81e1-d5f085be7862\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9a277259-2f15-4396-88b2-a9ffa1e11b22\">30cm 가 넘는 종양이 배에 있는데 그걸 지금 껏 모르고 지냈던 겁니다. 아... </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d5e7b03d-3921-4f49-9528-983df3d898b0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c2f42040-b555-4fd3-ba90-cdb17259891b\"><span class=\"__se-hash-tag\">#30cm</span></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5d5087f3-cd3e-493d-a785-343edfd4eb93\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bd369aa5-eced-4b01-ad50-61864c59d4b7\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cce2fc0c-d455-421e-b927-01e3c229d2cb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-344aeee2-d1c1-4900-b3a6-d300bb399198\">지난 주. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3cd74b08-e230-4947-810e-79db0b200845\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ae664d63-e566-4389-99b2-0d8f51660796\">환자분이 수술을 마치고 건강한 모습으로 한의원에 오셨습니다. 인사하러.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-643a0d8f-cc86-4b72-9fb6-f929f217eef7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d1643287-5f73-48bd-8fb7-a1586203094b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d6b0a3f5-bd50-4213-a468-2b3f1710debb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bf0c3c23-788f-4f65-b45b-8c1e7ad5a986\">선물도 사오셨네요 ^^</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-collage\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-collage\" id=\"SE-ef4f3d16-8943-4e36-b12b-cd67b66a75b8\">\n                            <div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n                                <div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n                                    \n                                    <div class=\"se-imageGroup-item se-imageGroup-col-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" id=\"SE-ee21a9a0-21ff-497c-9bbd-25a3e3904e1b\" class=\"se-module se-module-image __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"width:50.0%;\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-ee21a9a0-21ff-497c-9bbd-25a3e3904e1b\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxOTA3MDJfOTQg/MDAxNTYyMDM2OTcxODcx.bFE-s4xAUo60hwZOIvdiHD5OQCr5VuGKg0_0IJNpgqsg.aJpn1x-7Cuxjc4YdCdc7IFXf__AxVRG0qQOs7gO_NfQg.JPEG.isuhani/20190628_203811.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxOTA3MDJfOTQg/MDAxNTYyMDM2OTcxODcx.bFE-s4xAUo60hwZOIvdiHD5OQCr5VuGKg0_0IJNpgqsg.aJpn1x-7Cuxjc4YdCdc7IFXf__AxVRG0qQOs7gO_NfQg.JPEG.isuhani/